HSBC Inv Banking names Seoul corp finance director . HSBC Investment Bank Plc said on Monday it had appointed Kyungsup Song as director of corporate finance and equity capital markets of its Seoul branch with effect immediately . The appointment is the first move by HSBC Investment Banking , a unit of HSBC Holdings Plc , to establish an equity capital markets presence in Korea , and complements HSBC James Capel ' s broking operations in the country , it said . Song will be responsible for developing the investment bank ' s equity - linked securities business in Korea , HSBC Investment Banking said . Song was head of syndicate , capital markets of Daewoo Securities Co Ltd before joining HSBC Investment Banking , it said . - - Hong Kong Newsroom ( 852 ) 2843 6441 
